data.title: MG Mystics vs Stars
data.meta_description:
Take your pick of ticket options - either select & secure your seat in our Allocated Gold Zone OR find a seat on the day with our General Admission Blue Zone tickets. Join our Mystics Nation, secure your tickets now and be ‘Be the Crowd’ – we’ll see you there!

For Gold Allocated Seating please click on the SELECT YOUR SEATS tab to select your seat. If you have a valid promotion code click on the ‘Got a promo code? Click Here’ tab & enter.

For wheelchair seating inquiries, please call: 09 970 5201

We are taking on our Auckland rivals the Stars in the second match of the Barfoot & Thompson Northern Challenge.

Tickets include the curtain raiser between our Marvels and Comets in the Synergy Hair Netball League at 2pm.

Head along early and enjoy plenty of foyer activities and on court activations to entertain the whole family thanks to our match day partner MG Motor.

Doors Open: 1.30pm

Marvels vs Comets Game Begins: 2pm

Mystics vs Stars Game Begins: 4pm
